DialogueNode.dialogue: Hey there, Dave. How're you doing today?
I'm doing just fine, Alex! How are you?
I'm alright. I've got a busy day ahead of me, though.
Not bad. Say, could I ask you something?
Sorry to hear that. Let me know if there's anything I can do to help.
You know, now that you mention it... Could I ask you about something?
I received a report of issues with gender discrimination around the office. Is this something you've noticed at all?
I don't know... I mean, sure, sometimes some of the male employees can be a bit harsh, but I think that's just who they are. I'm not sure how much it has to do with gender.
Who exactly are you referring to?
Thanks, Dave. I'll look into that.
Anytime, Alex. Let me know if there's anything else I can do.
I'm not sure I'm comfortable getting caught up in this, Alex.
I completely understand. Thank you for your time, Dave. You've been very helpful.
You can tell me, Dave. It's just between us.
Alex, I'm really not comfortable with this. I'm gonna go back to work now.
